<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />You, Lord, are good, and ready to forgive,</para>

<para style="q1">and you show great mercy to all those who cry out to you.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />Yahweh, listen to my prayer;</para>

<para style="q1">hear the sound of my pleas.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />In the day of my trouble I call on you,</para>

<para style="q1">for you will answer me.</para>
